    \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CheckoutService/PlaceOrder操作延迟从正常15-15.6万秒激增至276-556万秒（延迟倍数>17倍），主要由于依赖CurrencyService转换失败\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"前端服务出现大量HTTP 500错误（195次），主要由于下游CurrencyService不可用导致订单处理失败\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**根因分析总结：**\n\n1. **主要根因**: CurrencyService服务完全不可用，其Convert操作延迟激增超过2000倍，并出现大量连接关闭错误（'transport is closing'）。\n\n2. **传播路径**: \n   - CurrencyService故障 → CheckoutService无法进行货币转换 → PlaceOrder操作失败 → Frontend返回HTTP 500错误\n\n3. **关键证据**:\n   - CurrencyService的Convert操作在异常期间完全不可用\n   - 错误消息明确显示\"failed to convert currency: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = transport is closing\"\n   - 所有依赖CurrencyService的服务都出现连锁故障\n\n4. **影响范围**: 主要影响结账流程，特别是涉及货币转换的订单处理操作。", "log_analysis_findings": "基于对日志数据的分析，我已经识别出了异常事件的根本原因。以下是详细的分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"context canceled\", \"RangeError\", \"Maximum call stack size exceeded\", \"conversion request failed\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"currencyservice 服务出现严重的 RangeError: Maximum call stack size exceeded 错误，导致货币转换功能完全失效\",\n      \"evidence\": \"conversion request failed: RangeError: Maximum call stack size exceeded\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"frontend 服务因 currencyservice 不可用而出现大量 context canceled 错误，无法完成货币转换和订单处理\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to do currency conversion for product X: rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 根因分析总结\n\n**主要异常模式**：\n\n1. **currencyservice 服务故障**：\n   - 出现大量 `RangeError: Maximum call stack size exceeded` 错误\n   - 这是 JavaScript 运行时错误，表示函数调用栈溢出\n   - 导致所有货币转换请求失败\n\n2. **frontend 服务连锁反应**：\n   - 由于 currencyservice 不可用，frontend 服务出现大量 `context canceled` 错误\n   - 影响包括：货币转换失败、订单完成失败、运费计算失败等\n\n**故障影响范围**：\n- 所有 frontend 实例（frontend-0, frontend-1, frontend-2）都受到影响\n- 所有 currencyservice 实例（currencyservice-0, currencyservice-1, currencyservice-2）都出现相同的栈溢出错误\n\n**建议解决方案**：\n1. 立即重启 currencyservice 服务以清除栈溢出状态\n2. 检查 currencyservice 代码中的递归调用或无限循环逻辑\n3. 增加 currencyservice 的监控告警，及时发现类似问题", "metric_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"server_error_ratio\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\",\n    \"timeout\",\n    \"request\",\n    \"response\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant increase in error_ratio (0.0 -> 1.6), server_error_ratio (0.0 -> 1.6), and rrt_max (235162.0 -> 60002068.0).\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio increased from 0.0 to 1.6, server_error_ratio increased from 0.0 to 1.6, rrt_max increased from 235162.0 to 60002068.0.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant increase in error_ratio (0.0 -> 1.82), server_error_ratio (0.0 -> 1.82), and rrt_max (258302.0 -> 60002525.0).\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio increased from 0.0 to 1.82, server_error_ratio increased from 0.0 to 1.82, rrt_max increased from 258302.0 to 60002525.0.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant increase in error_ratio (0.0 -> 1.06), server_error_ratio (0.0 -> 1.06), and rrt_max (275630.0 -> 60002627.0).\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio increased from 0.0 to 1.06, server_error_ratio increased from 0.0 to 1.06, rrt_max increased from 275630.0 to 60002627.0.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant increase in error_ratio (0.0 -> 28.87) and client_error_ratio (0.0 -> 28.87).\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio increased from 0.0 to 28.87, client_error_ratio increased from 0.0 to 28.87.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant increase in error_ratio (0.0 -> 2